        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>It won’t.</p>
<p>How many cuts have you made into your geometry? Too many cuts means too many surfaces, and the dynamic lighting goes wonky. If you’ve got too many, try making them func_detail’s, it <span class="bbcode-i">may</span> help.</p>
